reviews.review_text: Shotguns full of silver, bullets made of glass... On point sound here kiddo's..In a short year due to Garcia's health they boys whip out some magic in Oaktown~! Long interesting sets worth a listen..Forever Grateful>Forever Dead~!!! LIFER~~~Spread the love my friends for in 86 good shows are few and far between
